<Defs>

	<ThingDef ParentName="DryadBase">
		<defName>EMD_Awakened_Dryad_Bloomer</defName>
		<label>awakened bloomer dryad</label>
		<description>A dryad caste specialized in textile production. After awakening, it's capable of producing more textiles at a faster rate.\n\nAwakened dryads have both advantages and disadvantages compared to their bound relatives. While more proficient, specialized and unshackled, they can neither morph nor receive nourishment from a queen, resulting in a very limited lifespan.</description>
